        <div class="day">
            <div class="day__header">
                <span class="day__name">Friday, January 30</span>
            </div>
            <p>One more Therme session, then bus and train to Basel. Afternoon in the Altstadt: the Münster, the Marktplatz, the Rhine promenade.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="day">
            <div class="day__header">
                <span class="day__name">Saturday, January 31</span>
            </div>
            <p>Museum marathon. Morning at the <strong>Vitra Design Museum</strong> campus in Weil am Rhein—take the architecture tour if you can. Afternoon at <strong>Fondation Beyeler</strong>—allow at least three hours. Train to Zürich.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="lodging">
            <div class="lodging__name">B2 Hotel Zurich</div>
            <div class="lodging__address">Zürich</div>
