                <span class="day__name">Sunday, February 1</span>
            </div>
            <p>Quick Zürich morning: <strong>Fraumünster</strong> for Chagall's stained glass windows, Old Town, maybe the lake. Then the airport. Flight to London.</p>
            <p><em>Flight: British Airways BA719, ZRH 18:30 → LHR 19:15</em></p>
